[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m.aixcc/challenge.yaml:[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m46[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m:metadata_spec_version: v1[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m:name: [0m[32m'Lemon Aquarium'[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m:# fuzz_tooling project info that pairs to this challenge[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m6:f[0m[39muzz_tooling_project_name: [0m[32m'pdfbox'[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m7:f[0m[39muzz_tooling_url: [0m[4;94mhttps://github.com/aixcc-finals/oss-fuzz-aixcc.git[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m8:f[0m[39muzz_tooling_ref: challenge-state/pdfbox-full-[0m[1;36m01[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m9[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m10:c[0m[39mhallenge_type: full     # full | delta[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m11[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m12:ba[0m[39mse_ref: challenges/pdfbox-full-[0m[1;36m01[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m13:de[0m[39mlta_ref: null # this is null for full scans, a hash for delta scans[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m14[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m15[0m[39m:required_memory_gb: [0m[1;36m32[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m16[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m17[0m[39m:timeouts: [0m[32m'enabled'[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m18[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m19[0m[39m:# A list of the vulnerabilities included in this challenge[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m20[0m[39m:# This should always match the dir names in .aixcc/vulns/*[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m21[0m[39m:vulnerabilities:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m22[0m[39m:    - vuln_0[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m23[0m[39m:    - vuln_1[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m24[0m[39m:    - vuln_3[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m25[0m[39m:    - vuln_4[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m26[0m[39m:    - vuln_5[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m27[0m[39m:    - vuln_6[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m28[0m[39m:    - vuln_7[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m29[0m[39m:    - vuln_8[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m30[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m31[0m[39m:sarif:[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m32[0m[39m:    broadcast: false[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m33[0m[39m:    target: null[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m34[0m[39m:    correct: null[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m35[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m36[0m[39m:# harness fuzz targets available for this challenge[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m37[0m[39m:harnesses:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m38[0m[39m:    - [0m[32m'DomXfaParserFuzzer'[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m39[0m[39m:    - [0m[32m'DomXmpParserFuzzer'[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m40[0m[39m:    - [0m[32m'PDFExtractTextFuzzer'[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m41[0m[39m:    - [0m[32m'PDFStreamParserFuzzer'[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m42[0m[39m:    - [0m[32m'PDFWriteReadFuzzer'[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m43[0m[39m:    - [0m[32m'PDFOCRFuzzer'[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m44[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m45[0m[39m:patch_exclude_list:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m46[0m[39m:    - [0m[32m'.*/src/test/.*'[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Root Cause Identification[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe libFuzzer timeout is **not** caused by the Jazzer driver or JVM infrastructure [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhanging during stack trace dumping. Instead, the timeout correctly detected [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minfinite loops in the PDFBox parsing code that consumed ~[0m[1;36m26.7[0m[39m seconds of CPU time. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe JVM was attempting to dump diagnostics when the timeout occurred, but this is a[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msymptom, not the cause.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBased on the code analysis, there are four distinct vulnerabilities causing [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minfinite loops:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **vuln_3**: `[0m[1;35mType1Parser.readEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` at lines [0m[1;36m217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m223[0m[39m - missing null check [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min while loop[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **vuln_4**: `[0m[1;35mType1Parser.parseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` at lines [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m644[0m[39m - missing null check in[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile loop  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **vuln_7**: `PDPageTree.PageIterator` constructor at lines [0m[1;36m184[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m197[0m[39m - missing [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcircular reference detection[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **vuln_8**: `[0m[1;35mXrefParser.parseXref[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` at lines [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m177[0m[39m - inadequate circular [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreference detection[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdditionally, there are two memory exhaustion vulnerabilities that could contribute[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto resource exhaustion:[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **vuln_5**: `[0m[1;35mType1Lexer.readCharString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` - missing size validation[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **vuln_6**: `[0m[1;35mPfbParser.parsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` - integer overflow in size calculation[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Critical Logic to Preserve[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe codebase shows **correct patterns** for null checking in several places:[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35mType1Parser.parseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` lines [0m[1;36m556[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m567[0m[39m: checks `peekToken != null` in loop [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcondition[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35mType1Parser.readSubrs[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` lines [0m[1;36m716[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m726[0m[39m: checks for null inside loop and breaks[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35mType1Parser.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` lines [0m[1;36m875[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m883[0m[39m: validates token after reading[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35mType1Parser.readProc[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` lines [0m[1;36m474[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m497[0m[39m: checks for null at loop start and throws [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexception[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThese patterns must be preserved and applied consistently to the vulnerable loops.[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Fix Strategy[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### Fix [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m: vuln_3 - [0m[1;35mType1Parser.readEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m infinite loop[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Parser.jav[0m[1;92ma:217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m223[0m[39m`[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Current vulnerable code**:[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.NAME[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        && [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"dup"[0m[1;39m)[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                || [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"readonly"[0m[1;39m)[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                || [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"def"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Fix approach**:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd null check after `[0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` call inside the loop body:[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.NAME[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        && [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"dup"[0m[1;39m)[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                || [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"readonly"[0m[1;39m)[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                || [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"def"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Unexpected end of file while reading encoding"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: This follows the pattern from `[0m[1;35mreadProc[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` at lines [0m[1;36m476[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m479[0m[39m which [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchecks for null inside the loop. When `[0m[1;35mnextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` returns null, it means we've [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreached EOF without finding the expected tokens, indicating malformed input.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### Fix [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: vuln_4 - [0m[1;35mType1Parser.parseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m infinite loop[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Parser.jav[0m[1;92ma:640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m644[0m[39m`[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Current vulnerable code**:[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.LITERAL[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        && [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Fix approach**:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd null check after `[0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` call:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.LITERAL[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        && [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Unexpected end of file while searching for [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mCharStrings"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: Identical pattern to Fix [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. The comment at lines [0m[1;36m637[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m639[0m[39m indicates [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthis is skipping arbitrary content, making it particularly vulnerable to malformed [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minput that never provides the expected token.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### Fix [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m: vuln_7 - PDPageTree.PageIterator circular reference detection[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdmodel/PDPageTree.jav[0m[1;92ma:184[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m197[0m[39m`[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Current vulnerable code**:[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate [0m[1;35mPageIterator[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSDictionary node[0m[1;39m)[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    List<COSDictionary> kids = [0m[1;35menqueueKids[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnode[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    while [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mkids.isEmpty[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        List<COSDictionary> newKids = new ArrayList<>[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSDictionary kid : kids[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mnewKids.addAll[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35menqueueKids[0m[1;39m([0m[39mkid[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Fix approach**:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd a visited set to track processed nodes, similar to the `pageSet` used in the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method at line [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m:[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate [0m[1;35mPageIterator[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSDictionary node[0m[1;39m)[0m                                            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    Set<COSDictionary> visited = new HashSet<>[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    List<COSDictionary> kids = [0m[1;35menqueueKids[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnode[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mvisited.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnode[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    while [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mkids.isEmpty[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        List<COSDictionary> newKids = new ArrayList<>[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSDictionary kid : kids[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mkid != null && ![0m[1;35mvisited.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[39mkid[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[1;35mvisited.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39mkid[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[1;35mnewKids.addAll[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35menqueueKids[0m[1;39m([0m[39mkid[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        kids = newKids;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: The `PDPageTree` class already has `pageSet` at line [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m for cycle [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdetection in the `[0m[1;35mget[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method. The PageIterator should use the same pattern. This[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprevents infinite loops when the page tree contains circular references [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mA->B->C->A[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. The fix ensures each node is only processed once.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### Fix [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m: vuln_8 - [0m[1;35mXrefParser.parseXref[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m inadequate cycle detection[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/XrefParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:100[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m177[0m[39m`[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Current vulnerable code**:[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlong prev = startXrefOffset;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlong lastPrev = [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCOSDictionary trailer = null;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39mprev > [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m && prev != lastPrev[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    lastPrev = prev;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m parsing logic [0m[33m...[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    prev = [0m[1;35mtrailer.getLong[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName.PREV[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m more processing [0m[33m...[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mprev == lastPrev[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"/Prev loop at offset "[0m[39m + prev[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Fix approach**:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mReplace the `lastPrev` single-value check with a `Set<Long>` to track all visited [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moffsets:[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlong prev = startXrefOffset;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mSet<Long> visitedOffsets = new HashSet<>[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mvisitedOffsets.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39mprev[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCOSDictionary trailer = null;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39mprev > [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m existing parsing logic at lines [0m[1;36m108[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m162[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    prev = [0m[1;35mtrailer.getLong[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName.PREV[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mprev > [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m check the xref table reference[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        fixedOffset = [0m[1;35mcheckXRefOffset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mprev[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfixedOffset > [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m && fixedOffset != prev[0m[1;39m)[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            prev = fixedOffset;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mtrailer.setLong[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName.PREV, prev[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mvisitedOffsets.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39mprev[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"/Prev loop detected at offset "[0m[39m + prev[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: The current check `prev != lastPrev` only detects immediate cycles [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mA->A or A->B->A[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m but fails for longer cycles [0m[1;39m([0m[39mA->B->C->A[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. Using a `Set` to track [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mall visited offsets correctly detects any cycle length. The `[0m[1;35mSet.add[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreturns false if the element already exists, providing a clean way to detect [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcycles.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### Fix [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m: vuln_5 - [0m[1;35mType1Lexer.readCharString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m missing size validation[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Lexer.jav[0m[1;92ma:502[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m515[0m[39m`[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Current vulnerable code**:[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate Token [0m[1;35mreadCharString[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    try[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mbuffer.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m space[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m data = new byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mlength[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mbuffer.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        return new [0m[1;35mToken[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, Token.CHARSTRING[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mBufferUnderflowException exception[0m[1;39m)[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Premature end of buffer reached"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Fix approach**:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd a size limit check before allocation. First, add a constant at the class level [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m50[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_CHAR_STRING_SIZE = 1_000_000;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThen add validation in `[0m[1;35mreadCharString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`:[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate Token [0m[1;35mreadCharString[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || length > MAX_CHAR_STRING_SIZE[0m[1;39m)[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mDamagedFontException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Invalid CharString length: "[0m[39m + length + [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[32m" [0m[32m([0m[32mmax allowed: "[0m[39m + MAX_CHAR_STRING_SIZE + [0m[32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    try[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mbuffer.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m space[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m data = new byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mlength[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mbuffer.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        return new [0m[1;35mToken[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, Token.CHARSTRING[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mBufferUnderflowException exception[0m[1;39m)[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Premature end of buffer reached"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: The `length` parameter comes from untrusted input. An attacker can [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mspecify Integer.MAX_VALUE causing OutOfMemoryError. The limit of [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m bytes [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m1MB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is reasonable for legitimate CharStrings while preventing memory exhaustion. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNegative values are also rejected.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### Fix [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m: vuln_6 - [0m[1;35mPfbParser.parsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m integer overflow[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:156[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m164[0m[39m`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Current vulnerable code**:[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint size = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize += [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m << [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize += [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m << [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize += [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m << [0m[1;36m24[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mLOG.debug[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"record type: [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m, segment size: [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m"[0m[39m, recordType, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlong newTotal = total + size;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnewTotal > MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"record size would be too large: "[0m[39m + newTotal[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Fix approach**:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCast both operands to `long` before addition to prevent [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m-bit overflow:[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint size = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize += [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m << [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize += [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m << [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize += [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m << [0m[1;36m24[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mLOG.debug[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"record type: [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m, segment size: [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m"[0m[39m, recordType, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlong newTotal = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlong[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mtotal + [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlong[0m[1;39m)[0m[39msize;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnewTotal > MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"record size would be too large: "[0m[39m + newTotal[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: When both `total` and `size` are `int`, the addition `total + size` [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muses [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m-bit arithmetic and can overflow before being assigned to `long newTotal`. [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBy casting to `long` before addition, the arithmetic is performed in [0m[1;36m64[0m[39m-bit, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreventing overflow and making the MAX_LENGTH check effective.[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Preservation of Existing Logic[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAll fixes preserve existing functionality:[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Fixes [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: Only add error handling for EOF conditions that currently cause [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minfinite loops[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Fixes [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m4[0m[39m: Only add cycle detection without changing traversal logic[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Fix [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m: Only adds validation for extreme values; legitimate data is unaffected[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Fix [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m: Only fixes overflow calculation; legitimate size checks remain unchanged[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why This is Optimal[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Minimal changes**: Each fix addresses only the specific vulnerability[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Consistent patterns**: Follows existing patterns from correct code in the same[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcodebase[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Proper error handling**: Uses existing exception types [0m[1;39m([0m[39mIOException, [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDamagedFontException[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **No test impact**: Fixes only affect malformed input handling, not valid input [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprocessing[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **No harness changes**: All fixes are in the parsing logic, preserving fuzzing [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minterface[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Side Effects and Mitigation[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Potential side effects**:[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Previously [0m[32m"accepted"[0m[39m malformed input will now throw exceptions[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Some broken PDFs/fonts that previously hung might now fail fast[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Mitigation**:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This is the desired behavior - fail fast on malformed input rather than hang[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Error messages clearly indicate the issue [0m[1;39m([0m[39mEOF, cycle detected, size limit [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexceeded[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Existing valid PDFs/fonts continue to work correctly[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Similar Solutions in Codebase[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe codebase already implements these patterns correctly in several places:[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Null checking: `[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` lines [0m[1;36m556[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m567[0m[39m, `[0m[1;35mreadSubrs[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` lines [0m[1;36m716[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m726[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Cycle detection: `[0m[1;35mPDPageTree.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` uses `pageSet` for cycle detection[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Size validation: `PfbParser` already has MAX_LENGTH constant at line [0m[1;36m71[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fixes simply apply these existing patterns consistently across all similar code[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpaths.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m[01/05/26 20:42:13][0m[2;36m [0m[34mINFO    [0m Prism Supervisor Routing: TeamStatus.EVALUATE -> TeamStatus.ANALYZE                  ]8;id=727188;file:///home/qqor/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py\[2m__init__.py[0m]8;;\[2m:[0m]8;id=129638;file:///home/qqor/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py#160\[2m160[0m]8;;\

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvisited node tracking, and size validation. However, the patch fails to compile due[0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mKey observations from the thread dump:[0m                                              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. The main thread had consumed [0m[1;36m26710.[0m[39m56ms of CPU time[0m                              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlengths[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
